name: 2021 5th International Conference on Materials Engineering and Nano Sciences（ICMENS 2021）
content: Publication: All accepted papers of ICMENS 2021 will be published into IOP Conference Series: Materials Science and Engineering (ISSN: 1757-899X) which is indexed by Scopus, Conference Proceedings Citation Index—Science (CPCI-S) (Thomson Reuters, Web of Science), Chemical Abstracts etc.
